[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3559[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mstartOp[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"xmlNextElementSibling"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3560[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mincNodeIdx[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3561[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35msetNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35mxmlNextElementSibling[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mgetNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3562[0m[39m:                oomReport = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3563[0m[39m:                break;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3564[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3565[0m[39m:            case OP_XML_PREVIOUS_ELEMENT_SIBLING:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3566[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mstartOp[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"xmlPreviousElementSibling"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3567[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mincNodeIdx[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3568[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35msetNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, [0m[1;35mxmlPreviousElementSibling[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mgetNode[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3569[0m[39m:                oomReport = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3570[0m[39m:                break;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3571[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3572[0m[39m:            default:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3573[0m[39m:                break;[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3574[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3575[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3576[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mxmlFuzzCheckFailureReport[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvars->opName, oomReport, ioReport[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3577[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3578[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3579[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < REG_MAX; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3580[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mxmlFree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3581[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3582[0m[39m:    for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mi = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < REG_MAX; i++[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3583[0m[39m:        xmlNodePtr node = vars->nodes[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3584[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3585[0m[39m:        vars->nodes[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = NULL;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3586[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mdropNode[0m[1;39m([0m[39mnode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3587[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3588[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3589[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mxmlFuzzInjectFailure[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3590[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mxmlFuzzDataCleanup[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3591[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mxmlResetLastError[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3592[0m[39m:    [0m[1;35mreturn[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3593[0m[39m:[0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3594[0m[39m:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The double-free is triggered in the fuzz harness cleanup: it calls [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mxmlFree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mvars->strings[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mi[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` for each string register. Two registers can hold the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame pointer, so freeing both causes the AddressSanitizer error.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This happens because OP_XML_NODE_LIST_[0m[1;33mGET[0m[39m_STRING [0m[1;39m([0m[39mand likewise [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mOP_XML_NODE_LIST_[0m[1;33mGET[0m[39m_RAW_STRING[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m uses `[0m[1;35mmoveStr[0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, string[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, which stores the raw [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpointer returned by `xmlNodeListGetString` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mor `xmlNodeListGetRawString`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m without [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mduplicating it. If a client calls these APIs twice on the same node list, the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreturned buffer may be identical [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. an internal static buffer or reused [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, so two regs hold the same pointer.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The previous patch only modified `xmlNodeListGetRawString`, but the harness [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malso calls the unpatched `xmlNodeListGetString`. Moreover, even for raw, the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mduplicated buffer happens only once, and two calls to `xmlNodeListGetRawString` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mvia runtime patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m still return the same heap block and get freed twice.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Strategy Overview[0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure that every public string-returning API [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`xmlNodeListGetString` and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`xmlNodeListGetRawString`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m always returns a fresh heap allocation per call, so [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrepeated calls yield distinct pointers.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Concretely, wrap the existing implementation of `xmlNodeListGetString` in the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msame pattern applied to the raw variant: [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Internally call the core function which returns a temporary buffer.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m On non-NULL result, `xmlStrdup` that buffer into a new allocation.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Free the temporary buffer.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       d[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Return the new copy.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similarly, ensure that `xmlNodeGetContent` [0m[1;39m([0m[39malias of `xmlNodeListGetString`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand any other string-returning functions follow this duplicate-and-free pattern so [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcallers always get unique buffers.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Implementation Steps[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In tree.c, locate `xmlNodeListGetString` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround its definition[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Replace its[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbody:[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Replace direct calls to the internal buffer producer [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g. [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`xmlNodeListGetStringInternal`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with:[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            xmlChar *tmp = [0m[1;35mxmlNodeListGetStringInternal[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdoc, list, escMode[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp == NULL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m return NULL;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            xmlChar *ret = [0m[1;35mxmlStrdup[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mxmlFree[0m[1;39m([0m[39mtmp[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            return ret;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Remove or deprecate any variants that directly return buffers without [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mduplication.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Update documentation/comments to note that callers must free the returned [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstring [0m[1;39m([0m[39munchanged[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   d[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Run regression tests to verify that no existing tests break.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By guaranteeing fresh allocations per call, the fuzz harness registers will [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstore distinct addresses, preventing the double-free when cleaning up.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This preserves existing API semantics: callers still receive a heap buffer [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthey must free.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No harness or fuzz logic is modified—only core tree-handling code is adjusted.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Similar pattern already used in the raw variant [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`xmlNodeListGetRawString`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mensuring consistency across the API.[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Slight additional overhead: one extra `xmlStrdup` and `xmlFree` per call. This[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mis acceptable given fuzz use case and typical application loads.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Ensure that temporary buffers from internal functions are always [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap-allocated and safe to free. If any internal code returned static buffers, that[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmust be adjusted to return heap buffers or duplicated prior to free.[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - After patch, all callers [0m[1;39m([0m[39mincluding third-party code[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will see no API change: [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthey still receive a `xmlChar*` they must free.[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Validation[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rebuild libxml2 and the fuzz target.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Rerun the fuzzer; verify that no double-free occurs at the harness cleanup.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Run the full test suite to ensure no regressions.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
